listitem.para:
     In particular, if you get an error saying that a unique
     option is defined multiple times then you need to
     use the
     mkForce
     function. For example,

systemd.user.services.foo.Service.ExecStart = "/foo/bar";

     becomes

systemd.user.services.foo.Service.ExecStart = lib.mkForce "/foo/bar";

     We had to make this change because the old merging was causing too many
     confusing situations for people.
